section.def:
associated person (相聯者) has the meaning given by section 236(2) of the Ordinance;
                    (L.N. 130 of
            2019)

claimant
                (申索人) means a qualifying client who makes a claim
            under section 4;

subparagraph.content:
who has committed any breach of trust, defalcation, fraud or
                        misfeasance or assisted in the commission of a default by the specified
                        person or any other associated person of the specified person;

paragraph.content:
the specified securities or futures contracts or related assets are
                    entrusted to or received by the specified person or the associated person;
                    and
